text: Zapadny Okrug may refer to: *Western Administrative Okrug (Zapadny administrativny okrug), an administrative okrug of the federal city of Moscow, Russia *Zapadny Okrug, Belgorod, a city okrug of Belgorod, Belgorod Oblast, Russia *Zapadny Okrug, Krasnodar, a city okrug of Krasnodar, Krasnodar Krai, Russia
title: Zapadny Okrug
